'''托馬斯·愛德華·帕農'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Edward Pannone}}，{{IPAc-en|p|ɑː|ˈ|n|oʊ|n}} {{respell|pah|NOHN|'}};<ref>[http://www.milb.com/documents/3/7/0/239077370/2017_Western_All_Star_Roster_z8jt8hvn.pdf Western Division Player Roster, Eastern League 2017 All-Star Classic, Manchester, NH, Wednesday, July 12, 2017.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.milb.com/documents/3/7/0/239077370/2017_Western_All_Star_Roster_z8jt8hvn.pdf |date=20190804030601 }} Retrieved August 3, 2019</ref>，1994年4月28日）是一位美國[[職業棒球|職業棒球]][[投手|投手]]，現在是自由球員，先前曾於[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[多倫多藍鳥隊|多倫多藍鳥隊]]效力。

==高中與大學生涯==
帕農高中就讀於[[沃里克_(羅得島州)|沃里克]]的{{le|哈德里根主教中學|Bishop Hendricken High School}}，他在校隊的守備位置是[[外野手|外野手]]及投手<ref name="PannoneBRM">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=pannon000tho|title=Thomas Pannone Minor League Statistics & History|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115220906/https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=pannon000tho|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://scout.com/mlb/indians/Article/Pannone-benefitting-from-college-decisions-105226387|title=Pannone benefitting from college decisions|last=Tamburro|first=Ross|work=scout.com|date=July 11, 2015|accessdate=August 3, 2017}}</ref>。[[2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]會上，他在第33輪被[[芝加哥小熊隊|芝加哥小熊隊]]選中，但並未與球隊簽約而是選擇就讀{{le|南內華達學院|College of Southern Nevada}}<ref name="PannoneBRM"/>。在學院裡帕農沒有在繼續守外野，轉而專注在投球上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ohio.com/sports/rubberducks/a-former-outfielder-rubberducks-left-hander-thomas-pannone-making-his-mark-as-a-pitcher-1.774538|title=A former outfielder, RubberDucks left-hander Thomas Pannone making his mark as a pitcher|last=Bournival|first=Brad|work=ohio.com|date=June 14, 2017|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803010946/http://www.ohio.com/sports/rubberducks/a-former-outfielder-rubberducks-left-hander-thomas-pannone-making-his-mark-as-a-pitcher-1.774538|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在他唯一的{{le|大學棒球|college baseball}}賽季哩，他拿下6勝2敗的[[勝利投手|勝負紀錄]]、[[防禦率|防禦率]]1.84、53{{frac|2|3}}[[球局|投球局數]]、78次[[三振|三振]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thebaseballcube.com/players/profile.asp?P=thomas-pannone|title=Thomas Pannone Baseball Statistics|work=thebaseballcube.com|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804013157/http://www.thebaseballcube.com/players/profile.asp?P=thomas-pannone|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
===克里夫蘭印地安人隊===
[[2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]會上，[[克里夫蘭印地安人隊|克里夫蘭印地安人隊]]在第九輪選中帕農<ref name="PannoneBRM"/><ref name="PannoneDraft">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2017/06/thomas_pannone_looking_like_an.html|title=Thomas Pannone becoming Akron RubberDucks ace: Cleveland Indians Minor Leagues|last=Alexander|first=Elton|work=cleveland.com|date=June 23, 2017|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2018-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810072454/https://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2017/06/thomas_pannone_looking_like_an.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的職業初登板是代表[[美國職棒小聯盟#新人聯盟|新人聯盟]]的{{le|亞利桑那聯盟印第安人隊|Arizona League Indians}}出賽。在2013年賽季裡，他總共上場後援登場14次，留下1勝0拜、防禦率9.00、16局20次三振的成績<ref name="PannoneBRM"/>。2014年賽季他繼續在{{le|亞利桑那聯盟|Arizona League}}出賽，取得5勝0敗、防禦率3.20及45局62次三振的紀錄，還被聯盟選為季後賽全明星隊成員<ref name="PannoneBRM"/><ref name="PannoneMiLB">{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?sid=milb&player_id=623381#/career/R/pitching/2017/ALL|title=Thomas Pannone Stats, Highlights, Bio|work=MiLB.com|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205144700/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?sid=milb&player_id=623381#/career/R/pitching/2017/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，帕農迎來首次的完整賽季，代表[[美國職棒小聯盟#1A|1A]]的{{le|萊克縣隊長隊|Lake County Captains}}出賽投球，該年成績最終是出賽27場、投了116{{frac|1|3}}局、取得7勝6敗、防禦率4.02及120次三振<ref name="PannoneBRM"/>。2016年帕農從萊克縣隊長隊出發，該季還被選為季中全明星<ref name="PannoneMiLB"/>，隨後在七月就被升上[[美國職棒小聯盟#高階1A|高階1A]]的{{le|林奇堡山貓隊|Lynchburg Hillcats}}<ref name="PannoneBRM"/>。而2016年賽季他的戰績和季出賽25場，留下8勝5敗、防禦率2.57及133局122次三振的成績<ref name="PannoneBRM"/>。

2017年，帕農被指定在高階1A林奇堡山貓隊開始他的球季，同年五月初被升上{{le|2A等級|Double-A (baseball)|2A}}的{{le|阿克倫橡膠鴨隊|Akron RubberDucks}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsadvance.com/sports/hillcats/pannone-a-little-too-good-for-lynchburg/article_4cf21bba-3450-11e7-a645-4776bb5e15ce.html|title=Pannone a little too good for Lynchburg|last=Robertson|first=Mark D.|work=newsadvance.com|date=May 8, 2017|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206022432/https://newsadvance.com/sports/hillcats/pannone-a-little-too-good-for-lynchburg/article_4cf21bba-3450-11e7-a645-4776bb5e15ce.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在季中被選為[[東方聯盟|東方聯盟]]全明星隊成員<ref name="PannoneMiLB"/>。

===多倫多藍鳥隊===
2017年7月31日，帕農連同隊友薩馬德·泰勒（Samad Taylor）被交易到[[多倫多藍鳥隊|多倫多藍鳥隊]]，印地安人隊則是換回{{le|喬·史密斯 (投手)|Joe Smith (pitcher)|喬·史密斯}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/report-blue-jays-trade-reliever-joe-smith-indians/|title=Blue Jays trade reliever Joe Smith to Indians for prospects|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=July 31, 2017|accessdate=August 3, 2017|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206082938/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/report-blue-jays-trade-reliever-joe-smith-indians/|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨後他被指派到2A的{{le|新罕布夏漁夫貓隊|New Hampshire Fisher Cats}}，並在那裏完成剩下的賽季。通算2017年的成績，帕農取得9勝3拜、防禦率2.36、144{{frac|2|3}}局裡三振149次<ref name="PannoneBRM"/>。2017年11月20日，帕農被選入藍鳥隊的40人名單裡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/jansen-tellez-among-players-added-blue-jays-40-man-roster/|title=Jansen, Tellez among players added to Blue Jays’ 40-man roster|last=Davidi|first=Shi|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=November 20, 2017|accessdate=November 20, 2017|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205182832/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/jansen-tellez-among-players-added-blue-jays-40-man-roster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年3月16日，帕農被禁賽80場，原因是被檢測出{{le|脫氫氯甲基睪酮|Chlorodehydromethyltestosterone}}呈陽性反應，而該藥物是會提升運動表現的大聯盟禁藥<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-pannone-suspended-80-games-testing-positive-peds/|title=Blue Jays’ Pannone suspended 80 games after testing positive for PEDs|last=Nicholson-Smith|first=Ben|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=March 16, 2018|accessdate=March 16, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127045803/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-pannone-suspended-80-games-testing-positive-peds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在結束禁賽期後，帕農從[[3A等級|3A]]的{{le|布法羅野牛隊|Buffalo Bisons}}出發。8月9日，帕農被藍鳥隊叫上大聯盟<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-promote-pitching-prospect-thomas-pannone-triple/|title=Blue Jays promote pitching prospect Thomas Pannone from triple-A|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=August 9, 2018|accessdate=August 9, 2018|archive-date=2018-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181102034952/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-promote-pitching-prospect-thomas-pannone-triple/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月22日完成初登板，面對[[巴爾的摩金鶯隊|巴爾的摩金鶯隊]]前六局投出[[無安打|無安打]]的佳績，最終帕農奪得勝投，主投七局三振三次，只被擊出一支安打和投出兩次保送<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/thomas-pannone-allows-one-hit-in-first-start/c-291444498|title=Pannone throws a gem in first career start|last=Chisholm|first=Gregor|work=MLB.com|date=August 22, 2018|accessdate=August 23, 2018|archive-date=2018-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181019132729/https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/thomas-pannone-allows-one-hit-in-first-start/c-291444498|dead-url=no}}</ref>。帕農在2018年大聯盟先發6場，留下4勝1敗主投43局的成績。

帕農在2019年賽季以牛棚身分代表藍鳥隊出發。4月14日，帕農面對[[坦帕灣光芒隊|坦帕灣光芒隊]]投出[[完美一局|完美一局]]，僅以9球就先後三振掉[[阿法薩耶爾·賈西亞|阿法薩耶爾·賈西亞]]、[[布蘭登·勞爾|布蘭登·勞爾]]、{{le|丹尼爾·羅伯遜 (游擊手)|Daniel Robertson (shortstop)|丹尼爾·羅伯遜}}。這是藍鳥隊史上第三次的完美一局，前兩位投手是[[羅傑·克萊門斯|羅傑·克萊門斯]]及{{le|史蒂文·德拉巴爾|Steve Delabar}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ca.sports.yahoo.com/news/blue-jays-pannone-makes-history-with-immaculate-inning-193421916.html|title=Blue Jays’ Pannone makes fun-fact history with immaculate inning|last=Ashbourne|first=Nick|work=Yahoo! Sports Canada|date=April 14, 2019|accessdate=April 14, 2019|archive-date=2019-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415164621/https://ca.sports.yahoo.com/news/blue-jays-pannone-makes-history-with-immaculate-inning-193421916.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年8月24日，整季為出賽的帕農被藍鳥隊[[指定轉讓|指定轉讓]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/08/blue-jays-trent-thornton-injured-list-thomas-pannone-dfa.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121215604/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/08/blue-jays-trent-thornton-injured-list-thomas-pannone-dfa.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年11月2日，他成為自由球員。

